            <h5>HOW TO PROTECT YOURSELF?</h5>
            <h3>PREVENTION & ADVICE</h3>
            <p>
                There is currently no vaccine to prevent coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19).
                The best way to prevent<br> illness is to avoid being exposed to this virus.
                Stay aware of the latest information on the COVID-19<br> outbreak,
                available on the WHO website and through your national and local public health authority.
            </p>
            <div class="row prevent-info">
                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <img class="rounded-circle prevent-img"
                        src="images/gfx/advice-a.png"
                        alt="Advice image" width="120" height="120">
                    <h2>Wash your hands frequently</h2>
                    <p>Regularly and thoroughly clean your hands with
                         an alcohol-based hand rub or wash them with soap 
                         and water for at least 20 seconds.</p>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <img class="rounded-circle prevent-img"
                        src="images/gfx/advice-b.png"
                        alt="Advice image" width="120" height="120">
                    <h2>Maintain social distancing</h2>
                    <p>Maintain at least 1 metre (3 feet) distance between yourself & 
                        anyone who is coughing or sneezing. If you are too close, get chance to infected.</p>
                   
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <img class="rounded-circle prevent-img"
                        src="images/gfx/advice-c.png"
                        alt="Advice image" width="120" height="120">
                    <h2>Avoid touching face</h2>
                    <p>Hands touch many surfaces and can pick up viruses.
                     So, hands can transfer the virus to your eyes, nose or mouth and can make you sick.</p>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <img class="rounded-circle prevent-img"
                        src="images/gfx/advice-d.png"
                        alt="Advice image" width="120" height="120">
                    <h2>Practice respiratory hygiene</h2>
                    <p>Maintain good respiratory
                         hygiene as covering your mouth & nose with your 
                         bent elbow or tissue when cough or sneeze.</p>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

